    "description": "Created by three passionate indie-game lovers, we present to the world a new genre, a Puzzle Royale game! Our goal was to create a non-violent alternative to fun party games like Among Us or Pummel Party, that are easy to pick up and play with a group of friends.<br><br><strong>Welcome to Gloam!</strong><br>Play with 2–10 players in this online Puzzle Royale where your goal is to be the last player alight! Run around a haunted mansion, battling opponents to steal their life-force without perishing to the cold...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159960/extras/c0a7339d2306493d27cc3729372ddc4b.poster.avif?t=1711014935\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159960/extras/c0a7339d2306493d27cc3729372ddc4b.webm?t=1711014935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159960/extras/c0a7339d2306493d27cc3729372ddc4b.mp4?t=1711014935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You'll need good reflexes and quick-wits to win the fast-paced mini-games! Some which will require raw brainpower, some which are in need of speed, and others are asking for a little pinch of luck!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159960/extras/0b33044925e9bb4f3c6df601f04bbb5d.poster.avif?t=1711014935\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159960/extras/0b33044925e9bb4f3c6df601f04bbb5d.webm?t=1711014935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159960/extras/0b33044925e9bb4f3c6df601f04bbb5d.mp4?t=1711014935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect flames around the map to gain life and power your dash. Without it, you'll find it hard to escape from an unwanted battle, or you'll have a hard time catching up with your prey!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159960/extras/b05f1d1bb8418a5dd3c63a1164e832b8.poster.avif?t=1711014935\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159960/extras/b05f1d1bb8418a5dd3c63a1164e832b8.webm?t=1711014935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159960/extras/b05f1d1bb8418a5dd3c63a1164e832b8.mp4?t=1711014935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Gloam is a fun cross-platform party game suitable for all ages, that is free of violence or gore, and where we use our brains and agility to out-wit our opponents. Matches are best enjoyed among friends, who can join-in for free via the Android version of the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159960/extras/ca5fb145d84bf84b4d8d68ae50be6894.poster.avif?t=1711014935\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159960/extras/ca5fb145d84bf84b4d8d68ae50be6894.webm?t=1711014935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159960/extras/ca5fb145d84bf84b4d8d68ae50be6894.mp4?t=1711014935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If you perish, come back as a ghost and have fun annoying the survivors by freezing the rooms they are in! You will no longer be able to win the game, but maybe you could influence who does... sneaky!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159960/extras/d4c01d455a71ef7a04e98aaddbf12dfc.poster.avif?t=1711014935\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159960/extras/d4c01d455a71ef7a04e98aaddbf12dfc.webm?t=1711014935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159960/extras/d4c01d455a71ef7a04e98aaddbf12dfc.mp4?t=1711014935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>8 mini-games, with a lot more to be added before the end of early access.<br></li><li>Play privately with friends or in online public matches.<br></li><li>Customize your character: Colour, skin, and gravestone.<br></li><li>Cross-platform play between PC.</li></ul>",
